Delego Wallet is a next-generation **smart wallet (account abstraction wallet)** designed for seamless, gasless, and secure Web3 transactions. It removes the complexity of private keys, gas fees, and manual transaction handling â€” making crypto as easy as using UPI.

Built for hackathons, startups, and real-world adoption.

