## ğŸ”¥ Why Delego Wallet?

Traditional wallets require:
- Managing private keys
- Paying gas fees
- Signing every transaction manually

Delego Wallet solves this with:
- Smart Accounts (ERC-4337)
- Gasless transactions
- Session-based authorization
- Programmable wallet logic

