## ğŸ” Smart Wallet Concept

Delego Wallet uses **Smart Accounts** instead of EOAs.

### Benefits:
- No private key management
- Recoverable wallet
- Programmable security
- Automated transactions

### Run:

# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/jeevagan-dev/defy-26.git
cd defy-26

# Install smart contract dependencies
cd smart-contract
npm install

# Compile & deploy smart contracts using Hardhat
npx hardhat compile
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network sepolia

# Install expo app dependencies
cd ../app
npm install

# Run expo app
npm run dev

